</b>Agenda item 4 
<b>Human rights situations that require the Council&#8217;s attention 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Albania</b>*<b>, Australia</b>*<b>, Austria</b>*<b>, Belgium, Bosnia and Herzegovina</b>*<b>, Bulgaria</b>*<b>, Canada</b>*<b>, 
